definition.value: A immortal human ovary-derived fibroblast cell line cell that has the characteristics: Granulosa cell tumor. Possible to produce progesterone after HCG addition. Cell growth is slow.
Derived from tissue: ovary, peritoneum in animal: human.
Originator: Nishi, Yoshihiro & Nawata, Hajime
Register: Nishi, Y. & Nawata, H.
